        <!-- 1. Eligibility -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">1. Eligibility</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            To access and use our Service, you must be at least 18 years old. By using our Service, you represent and warrant that you meet this age requirement, and that you have the legal capacity and authority to enter into a binding contract. Our Service is currently available only in the United States and made specifically for payors, health systems, providers and consumers. Any other usage must be authorized by Payerset in advance in writing. We reserve the right to limit access to our Service based on your location, and we may block access to the Service from outside the United States at our discretion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Accounts and Access -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">2. Accounts and Access</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
