          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. License Grant -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">3. License Grant</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Subject to the terms and conditions of these Terms we grant you a limited, nonexclusive, nontransferable license to use the Service. All proprietary rights, including intellectual property rights, in the Service will remain the property of Payerset. You agree and acknowledge that Payerset may use anonymized, aggregated usage metrics to improve the Service.
