          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-dark mb-4">5. Subscription and Payment</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            a. Our Service is provided through annual subscriptions. You are required to pay the full subscription fee before access to the Service is granted. We reserve the right to modify our pricing and payment terms at any time, with or without prior notice for any renewal.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
